<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gab's Scrapbook</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script:wght@700&family=Homemade+Apple&family=Special+Elite&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #e6dfcf; /* Vintage Paper Tone */
            --ink: #2b2621;
            --accent-green: #6b7c62;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            background-image: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/papyrus.png');
            color: var(--ink);
            font-family: 'Special Elite', serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        /* Layout Grid */
        .scrapbook {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            grid-template-rows: auto auto auto;
            gap: 30px;
            max-width: 1100px;
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Header Section */
        header {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 40px;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
            font-size: 5rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .paper-scrap {
            background: #fdfaf0;
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            position: relative;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        /* Polaroid Effect for Artists */
        .polaroid-gallery {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .polaroid {
            background: white;
            padding: 15px 15px 40px 15px;
            box-shadow: 3px 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 180px;
            text-align: center;
            transform: rotate(-2deg);
        }

        .polaroid:nth-child(even) { transform: rotate(3deg); }

        .polaroid img { width: 100%; height: 180px; object-fit: cover; }

        .polaroid p { 
            font-family: 'Homemade Apple', cursive; 
            margin-top: 15px; 
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* Hover Detail Effect */
        .polaroid-detail {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
        }

        .polaroid:hover { transform: scale(1.1) rotate(0deg); z-index: 10; }
        .polaroid:hover .polaroid-detail { opacity: 1; }

        /* About Me Scrap */
        .about-me {
            grid-column: 2;
            transform: rotate(1deg);
            clip-path: polygon(2% 0%, 98% 1%, 100% 98%, 1% 100%);
        }

        /* Playable Songs Scrap */
        .favorite-songs {
            grid-column: 1;
            transform: rotate(-1.5deg);
        }

        .song-row { margin-bottom: 10px; cursor: pointer; }
        .yt-player { display: none; margin-top: 10px; }
        .song-row:hover .yt-player { display: block; }

        /* Decorations */
        .flower { position: absolute; width: 80px; opacity: 0.6; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .scrapbook { display: block; }
            .polaroid-gallery { flex-wrap: wrap; }
            .paper-scrap { margin-bottom: 30px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="scrapbook">
    <header>
        <h1>Gab</h1>
        <p>— A soul full of stories and dreams —</p>
    </header>

    <div class="polaroid-gallery">
        <div class="polaroid">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/Clairo.jpg" alt="Clairo">
            <p>Clairo</p>
            <div class="polaroid-detail">
                <strong>Clairo</strong><br>Contemporary indie-pop favorite.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="polaroid">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/CocteuTwins.jpg" alt="Cocteau Twins">
            <p>Cocteau Twins</p>
            <div class="polaroid-detail">
                <strong>Cocteau Twins</strong><br>Masters of the ethereal dream pop sound.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="polaroid">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/WeyesBlood.jpg" alt="Weyes Blood">
            <p>Weyes Blood</p>
            <div class="polaroid-detail">
                <strong>Weyes Blood</strong><br>Sophisticated baroque pop melodies.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <article class="paper-scrap about-me">
        <h3 style="font-family: 'Homemade Apple', cursive;">About Me</h3>
        <p>Hello! I'm Gabriel.</p>
        [span_0](start_span)[span_1](start_span)<p>I am a 20-year-old **2nd year Nursing Student** at **Bicol University Tabaco**[span_0](end_span)[span_1](end_span).</p>
        [span_2](start_span)<p>An old soul who adores binge-watching films, sleeping, and of course, a true **Fleabag enthusiast**[span_2](end_span).</p>
    </article>

    <article class="paper-scrap favorite-songs">
        <h3 style="font-family: 'Homemade Apple', cursive;">Favorite Songs</h3>
        <div class="song-row">
            ▸ <strong>Harbor</strong> <br><small>Clairo</small>
            <div class="yt-player">
                <iframe width="100%" height="150" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6m6S_6B2Iaw" frameborder="0"></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="song-row">
            ▸ <strong>Rilkean Heart</strong> <br><small>Cocteau Twins</small>
            <div class="yt-player">
                <iframe width="100%" height="150" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7V-M7qBvG8A" frameborder="0"></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
</div>

</body>
</html>

